      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIKE A ROCK (5) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in five starts, including three wins and two placings. Comes off a (25.93) win last time, scoring by 1.75 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 460m at Warragul. Expected to be in the finish. LAKEVIEW CINDY (8) was a last start winner (28.73) at Sale who is building a strong winning record. Form at the trip excellent including two wins. One of main contenders. PAW CORNELIUS (7) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.9 lengths at Shepparton in a handy 21.97 beating Bailieston. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Likely to be in the finish. PERFECTLY (1) is always a threat when she races at this journey.",
